snippet.textDisplay: I’m really spiraling off the grid. Guarded and then open then guarded then open. Why? It’s because of my twin flame. He draws me close then rejects me. Then draws me close then rejects me. Literally this last month I went through hell internally dealing with not only my stuff but his stuff too. Then he gets hurt because I react? Like, am I not allowed to feel a response? Last night was horrible. The things said on his live show might as well put a dagger inside my heart. He was not even acting like he even cared. If it’s entertainment to be very ruthless, okay. But He should have reminded himself about how I read into the things he says as if it’s directed at me sometimes. And why? Because he refuses to talk directly to me. He plays mind games with me. It’s very painful and now last night I got very pissed. I didn’t say anything to cause damage. Before bed I calmed down. When I woke up I thought, well maybe I’ll let it go. This anger is still underneath the surface. I guess I just need to vent it before I honestly can have any peace. I’ll do it here.  My point is, we can go round and around with these mind games but the fact of the matter is when it comes to true love, you should never be mean or deliberately try to push someone intentionally away. Realizing we are not perfect. But how many times getting rejected and feeling hurt do you honestly believe someone as special as me would put up with even if you are my DM.? It’s madness. If you were anyone else I honestly would have been gone much sooner. Dude, get yourself together. Figure out what the hell you want. Do you want love or do you want to hide behind it making yourself miserable? You try to push me away but really all you are doing is making yourself miserable. You are sabotaging you and making my life living hell and torment. No love. No appreciation for all the selfless sacrifices and devotion. Dude...seriously that’s f’ed up. You can’t possibly believe I’m sticking around for this emotional abuse like it’s endless until you decide at some random time? I think I’ll be too ground down into nothing by then. This impacts my self worth. It’s nuts. I’m not sure why on earth God would ever make me stick around to this. It’s crazy! I told God I’ll let go of the anger and try to be patient one more freaking time. But! I do have the right to enact my free will and sever the ties forever. It would seem by the way he treats me that THIS IS what he wants me to do. Yes you! My tf. You want me to leave you for good. That’s what your behavior says to me.   Anyways, I’m not going to show my YouTube history or leave any songs right now because Im hurting. I need time to do what I said. Try one more time.  I’ll start by listening to this song as many times as I have to even if it’s all day and night. I’ll feel better.ill wait to see what goes on but know this is it. Please get it together.
